## AI Agent Tool Registration

**Tool description** (paste into the AI Agent node's Tool 6 entry):

> Compute the full forecast and read all source files internally. Call ONCE
> per forecast — do not call Tool 4 first. Parameters: propertyCode (string,
> e.g. "prop01"), period (string, e.g. "2026-Q3"), fiscalYear (string, e.g.
> "FY2026"). Returns a small summary object (fileName, driveLink, tabs,
> keyFindings) — the full forecastData JSON stays internal to this tool and
> is never passed back through the agent. Do NOT call Calculator. Do NOT call
> Tool 4 or a separate "Generate Excel" tool — there is no separate
> Excel-generation step.

**Input fields:** `propertyCode`, `period`, `fiscalYear` — all set to **From
AI** with per-field descriptions (not static Mapping values), so the agent
fills them dynamically from the conversation.

